extendedInfo.description: Application based on IOSched and GDDSched. With this app, you can consult the online Campus Party Brazil 2011 calendar and also share with your friends. Compatible with Android 2.0 or higher.CampusTV link. Adobe Flash 10.1 required.Don't get lost! Map included.Need Internet access.Keywords:cpbr4, campusparty, cpbr2011
